As a Fanclub founder of @orangearmyforever , met @mutyalureddykaki Garu - Father of NKR and congratulated him for the efforts he kept to deliver a Star @nitishkumarreddy to Indian cricket and Sunrisers.

Introduced all our Fanclub members to him and spent a quality of time as he discussed about NKR journey from his young age and his hardwork as a father to support NKR vision.

Thank you very much @mutyalureddykaki sir one again for this time..
